{"tid":864454,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[調查]麻煩各位幫幫手做個有關戒口嘅調查","createTime":"2018-10-16T08:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T10:33:06.000Z","uid":216961,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"176bb0cca0e3415881b712297ecbeacb1768982a","tid":864454,"uid":216961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"各位唔好意思，我做緊個project，希望了解及統計香港市民嘅戒口習慣，以及用膳/購物時有否關心及留意產品嘅內容，從而設計一個方案去幫助大家更加注重健康。<br />\n<br />\n所以個統計對於我個project非常重要，跪求大家幫忙花少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/dZU4wzXs908ZKm5p1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FdZU4wzXs908ZKm5p1&d=4ca4e27lY2GGV30PmgtKiP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f176d16b\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/dZU4wzXs908ZKm5p1</a>"},{"pid":"a8ce33d61cda55d6d6c06225a5aec3e37d88a12f","tid":864454,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"一啲誠意都無 點幫？"},{"pid":"f62a530984103b934e69a77ab5e7087fbcb8a6a4","tid":864454,"uid":216961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8ce33d61cda55d6d6c06225a5aec3e37d88a12f","tid":864454,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"一啲誠意都無 點幫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣會有誠意啲？J圖定seed？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028d1700e0c0b1348bc8b5637018561c89c4e929","tid":864454,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f62a530984103b934e69a77ab5e7087fbcb8a6a4","tid":864454,"uid":216961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8ce33d61cda55d6d6c06225a5aec3e37d88a12f","tid":864454,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re